page.title: 21Darlington Central East
page.content: Darlingtons population has now increased to 107,000. The Market Square used to house the outdoor market stalls on a Monday and Saturday. It has now been refurbished and has been moved to West Rowe and Northgate. The Market Square is now surrounded by cafes and pubs. In July and August, there is entertainment in the square, such as tea dancers and a summer spectacular for the children.
